dataIdInfo.idPurp: Dataset developed for E-9-1-1 addressing purposes: to assign new addresses; to verify existing addresses; to ensure current addresses are in sequence and addressed off of access road; and for usage by Emergency Personnel. Data meets Version 2.0 of the NENA GIS Data model and can be used for GIS data exchange between neighboring public safety agencies and meets the requirements of GIS data needed for NENA i2 solution (NENA 08-001), and for the Location Validation Function and Emergency Calling Routing Function in the NENA i3 solution (NENA 08-751)
dataIdInfo.idAbs: Dataset contains points for addresses within Alachua County, Florida. The Alachua County E-9-1-1 Office assigns and maintains addresses for all of Alachua County with the exception of the Town of Micanopy. Micanopy assigns addresses within its municipal boundary.
dataIdInfo.idCredit: Alachua County Fire Rescue, E-9-1-1 Communication Branch
